### Quick start checklist (project-specific)

- Read `.github/copilot-instructions.md` and `00-repository-overview.mdc`.
- For new routes: implement `generateMetadata` using `generatePagesData` and `buildPageMeta`.
- For list pages: fetch via `lib/api/*` and use `insertAds` on SSR only; append client items without ads.
- For filters/URLs: use `utils/url-filters.ts` helpers; never craft strings manually.
- For scripts/JSON-LD: read `nonce` from `headers()` and pass to `<Script>`.
- For images: use the image wrapper in `components/ui/common/image` and quality/size helpers.
- Before PR: `yarn typecheck && yarn lint && yarn test`.
